321
00:34:16,420 --> 00:34:18,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ali druga stvar, ova psihoza.

322
00:34:19,139 --> 00:34:20,579
[SPEAKER_01] koje ljudi neprekidno žive.

323
00:34:20,579 --> 00:34:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

324
00:34:21,099 --> 00:34:22,980
