348
00:35:18,659 --> 00:35:21,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si za Franklov pristup.

349
00:35:21,980 --> 00:35:23,599
[SPEAKER_01] paradoksne intencije.

350
00:35:23,599 --> 00:35:24,440
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da, tako.

351
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:26,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, ja te se ne bojim.

352
00:35:26,219 --> 00:35:30,280
