798
00:50:42,159 --> 00:50:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, centralni komitet

799
00:50:43,199 --> 00:50:44,039
[SPEAKER_00] Savjeza komunista

800
00:50:44,039 --> 00:50:45,619
